FBIS4-61213 "drsov087_b_94008" FBIS-SOV-94-087 Daily Report 5 May 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Issues Labor Protection Edict Yeltsin Issues Labor Protection Edict LD0505053994 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 0200 GMT 5 May 94 LD0505053994 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Russian BFN [Text] Boris Yeltsin has issued an edict relating to state supervision and monitoring of the observance of legislation on labor and labor protection. The edict is aimed at ensuring guarantees of the constitutiional right of citizens to work in conditions corresponding to the requirements of safety and hygiene.
